{"id": "1399607443755106354", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "||大概是异世界利莫里亚没完全亡国，余孽们点了几千年的蹈海者教育科技树吧x\n米粒父亲要是有这个程度的理智，大家开开心心包饺子应该都没后面啥事了||", "timestamp": "2025-07-29T04:20:18.040000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
